regexp
Class OwnStack<E>

java.lang.Object
  regexp.OwnStack<E>

public class OwnStack<E>
extends java.lang.Object

The OwnStack specifies an explicit implementation of Stack, as demanded by Matti Luukkainen for the Data Structures Project course. The functionality is equal to your run-of-the-mill generic stack structure.
